---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Reference" description="Background, conventions, and machine-generated documentation">
  <section class="gw-section">
    <div class="gw-width gw-stack--lg">
      <div class="gw-prose">
        <h1 class="gw-heading-l">Reference</h1>
        <p>Background material: architecture decisions, project conventions, and generated documentation for the public API.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="gw-grid">
        <article class="gw-card gw-stack--sm">
          <h2 class="gw-heading-s"><a class="gw-link" href="/reference/principles/">Principles</a></h2>
          <p class="gw-body--sm">The five design principles every API and token decision is measured against.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="gw-card gw-stack--sm">
          <h2 class="gw-heading-s"><a class="gw-link" href="/reference/glossary/">Glossary</a></h2>
          <p class="gw-body--sm">Canonical terms used across the API, patterns, and documentation.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="gw-card gw-stack--sm">
          <h2 class="gw-heading-s"><a class="gw-link" href="/reference/adr/">Architecture decision records</a></h2>
          <p class="gw-body--sm">Load-bearing decisions, with the alternatives that were considered and rejected.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="gw-card gw-stack--sm">
          <h2 class="gw-heading-s"><a class="gw-link" href="/reference/api/">API reference</a></h2>
          <p class="gw-body--sm">Generated TypeScript reference for the public component API.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="gw-card gw-stack--sm">
          <h2 class="gw-heading-s"><a class="gw-link" href="/reference/conventions/flows-as-tests/">Flows as human-testable documentation</a></h2>
          <p class="gw-body--sm">Why every Flow is paired with a visible test script.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="gw-card gw-stack--sm">
          <h2 class="gw-heading-s"><a class="gw-link" href="/reference/conventions/ui-review/">UI review workflow</a></h2>
          <p class="gw-body--sm">How the local UI review script supports human inspection.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="gw-card gw-stack--sm">
          <h2 class="gw-heading-s"><a class="gw-link" href="/reference/design-tokens-format/">Design Tokens Community Group reference</a></h2>
          <p class="gw-body--sm">How Groundwork's token source files map to the DTCG format.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DocsLayout>
